# mapOverlayLevel(level:)

**Instance Method**

Specifies the position of overlays relative to other map content.

## Declaration

```swift
@MainActor @preconcurrency func mapOverlayLevel(level: MKOverlayLevel) -> some MapContent

```

## Parameters

- **level**: One of the [doc://com.apple.mapkit/documentation/MapKit/MKOverlayLevel] levels.

## Return Value

Returns [doc://com.apple.mapkit/documentation/MapKit/MapContent] with overlays drawn with the positioning level you specified.
